Jim Broadbent is an actor who played two minor characters in the Primary Phase of the radio series, Vroomfondel and Shooty, then returned in the Hexagonal Phase to play Marvin after the previous actor, Stephen Moore, retired. 

He has won several awards over his acting career.Further reading
